divs: sighting detailsi have spotted a u.f.o. in a frame of "crank" movie dvd . the frame can be found at : scene 13 of 25 (13\25) at 2 minutes and 16 seconds past scene 13 . 1-press the "display" button on the remote . 2-press next until 13\25 is displayed on top of the screen and then wait untill the number next to it shows : 2:16 and the press "pause" . you will spot a small stationary object hovering in the sky , near middle of the screen . 3- you can press "zoom" to get a better look at the object .
Summary: U.F.O. spoted in a major U.S. movie ?
